"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Metaverse land sales [topped $100 million](https://decrypt.co/87388/metaverse-land-nft-sales-ethereum-solana) this week alone. That included [$2.43 million](https://decrypt.co/86921/decentraland-virtual-land-plot-sells-record-2-43-million) for a parcel of land in Decentraland, and a [record $4.3 million](https://markets.businessinsider.com/news/currencies/metaverse-property-sandbox-virtual-real-estate-deal-record-4-million-2021-11) for real estate in The Sandbox.\\n\\nIt might be tempting to dismiss all this metaverse madness as the latest internet spending bubble, but the data points are adding up. The metaverse is growing, it's a real thing, and many, many people are going to spend many, many hours there in the future.\\n\\nThe Sandbox isn't even fully live yet; it launched an alpha test this week. No matter: Its token SAND is up 82% in the past month, while Decentraland's token MANA is up 35% in a month. The irony of [Facebook's rebrand to Meta](https://decrypt.co/84721/facebook-metaverse-new-company-name-meta-nft) is that while crypto people mocked the company—and its stock suffered—its embrace of the metaverse [boosted metaverse tokens](https://decrypt.co/86768/ethereum-metaverse-tokens-keep-climbing-mana-sand-hit-all-time-highs).\",\"timestamp\":1638701696,\"title\":\" to be right\"},\"digest\":\"E1-ig81whH2LWy98wglBg2d6bFlQW2DDL3gixp-syBg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2F354aDa47174376a144b74059551f6adC6B1427\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ouPt23KVUWcm4pApqa-uu2iLqzOMZT9l2i378tEGoQI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_tcdL-FZO_RdKIilZwEfdNwMRknipnwbChpk2HQ9lLQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"9SPmrObuUiZj7g6Eqa4B7n1xm7lCLFx2oT4ecyjj-h7_nday7GL_1Lwl6qdM0XAEZCjsH4lpFnCww1_aIRlKjQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe3a7e3eb7b7d9f8e334b019e2b540fc1d653b655e1cf85015586b673d330719a60cc12ba9316f77d5c23ba209a248feeb5f337767d81d3776b7936a5f2b9821e1b\",\"signingKeyMes